    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Write invisible notes on just about any surface with the ASR Federal Security Spy UV Invisible Ink Permanent Marker Pens, with markings remaining invisible until illuminated by a UV light source. The spy pens can write invisibly on almost any dry surface, including metal, wood, plastic, paper, glass, paint, skin, clothing and even currency. If digital or regular written communication are not a viable form of communication available, look no further than these UV invisible ink permanent marker pens. The invisible ink pens are ideal for making and communicating sensitive information, marking personal property or monitoring theft detection. They will come in handy in all sorts of espionage or covert situations</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Ultraviolet UV Theft Detection Pen Invisible Ink Security Marker 3 Colors</h2>\n  <p>Write invisible notes on just about any surface with the ASR Federal Security Spy UV Invisible Ink Permanent Marker Pens, with markings remaining invisible until illuminated by a UV light source. The spy pens can write invisibly on almost any dry surface, including metal, wood, plastic, paper, glass, paint, skin, clothing and even currency.</p>\n  <p>If digital or regular written communication are not a viable form of communication available, look no further than these UV invisible ink permanent marker pens. The invisible ink pens are ideal for making and communicating sensitive information, marking personal property or monitoring theft detection. They will come in handy in all sorts of espionage or covert situations.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>INVISIBLE INK PENS:</strong> Communicating covert written messages or avoiding a digital footprint? Look no further than the ASR Federal Security Spy UV Invisible Ink Permanent Marker Pens; Ideal for sensitive notes, marking personal property and theft detection, the invisible ink pens can write without detection on almost any dry surface</li>\n    <li><strong>ELECTION CERTIFIED:</strong> Used by local and federal government agencies; election certified invisible ink pens and markers for voting stations and election related events; the markings will remain invisible until illuminated under a UV light</li>\n    <li><strong>HOME SECURITY:</strong> Due to the nature of the invisible ink, mark valuable personal property without damage; if altered or tampered with, reveal with a UV light or other black light source</li>\n    <li><strong>FUN FOR KIDS:</strong> A fun activity for kids, the invisible ink allows for fun secret messages to be shared between friends; safe and harmless, the spy pens are nontoxic, waterproof, heatproof and can mark over 2500 feet in length</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Length: 5 inches; Pen Type: Marker with felt tip; Colors: Blue, Pink and Green; Blue and pink inks are oil based; Green ink is water based</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/Professional_Equipment/UVM_UV_Pens_YLW_detail_02.jpg\" alt=\"Write invisible notes on just about any surface with the ASR Federal Security Spy UV Invisible Ink Permanent Marker Pens, with markings remaining\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> UVPEN</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 766359799148</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The spy pens are also great for home security; enhance the security of your personal property without causing any damage; simply mark a desired item and if you suspect it has been tampered or altered with, simply illuminate with a UV light or black light to reveal any potential changes or alterations.</p>\n  <p>Lastly, the invisible ink pens are also a fun activity for kids. They’ll love the playing with the invisible ink to share secret messages and are sure to conjure up some fun pretend play adventures between siblings and friends. Safe and harmless, the spy pens are nontoxic, waterproof, heatproof and can mark over 2500 feet in length.</p>\n  <p>These invisible ink pens are excellent tools for local and federal governments alike, as the markings will remain invisible until illuminated under a UV light. Election certified invisible ink pens and markers are suitable for voting stations, ballot boxes and other election related events.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
